    "abstractNote": "This article provides short blographic information about Bardaisan (154-222/223) and discusses the problem of authorship of the work \"The Book of the Laws of Countries\". ln the main part the \u0410. considers the value of key concepts of Bardaisan - fate, nature and freedom, which then in detail \u0430 \u0433\u0435 considered in the context of Bardaisan's doctrine. ln the conclusion of the article the importance of the doctrine of Bardaisan anti-fatalistic and anti-astrological polemic is defined and \u0430n Orthodox assessment of the ideology of the Syrian writer is given.",
